Platinum Group Metals Ltd.


            
            Platinum Group Metals Ltd. is a mining company, which is focused on production, development and exploration of platinum and palladium. Its projects include Maseve Mine and Waterberg. The company was founded by R. Michael Jones on February 18, 2002 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




